{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T15:53:35.034Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Web Search tool"},{"type":"text","text":" is a server-side Anthropic-defined tool in Claude's Web Tools suite that gives Claude direct access to real-time web content, enabling it to answer questions with up-to-date information beyond its training knowledge."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The web search tool ("},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"web_search_20260209"},{"type":"text","text":") is one of four "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"server tools"},{"type":"text","text":" Anthropic provides (along with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"code_execution"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"web_fetch"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_search"},{"type":"text","text":") that run entirely on Anthropic's infrastructure. When Claude uses it, you see the results directly without handling execution yourself."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Real-time information"},{"type":"text","text":": Claude can access current news, research, prices, and events beyond its knowledge cutoff"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reduced agent complexity"},{"type":"text","text":": Agents no longer need to make queries, pull results into context, fetch HTML files, and reason over them separately—Claude handles this internally"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Improved accuracy"},{"type":"text","text":": Dynamic filtering during searches improves performance on benchmarks like BrowseComp (Sonnet 4.6: 33.3% → 46.6%; Opus 4.6: 45.3% → 61.6%)"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How it works"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool declaration"},{"type":"text","text":": You add the tool to your API request:"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"``"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"python tools=[{\"type\": \"web_search_20260209\", \"name\": \"web_search\"}] "},{"type":"text","text":"`"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\n2. **Automatic triggering**: With "},{"type":"text","text":"tool_choice={\"type\": \"auto\"}`, Claude decides when to call it—typically when the request maps to web search capability and the answer isn't already in context\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Server execution"},{"type":"text","text":": Anthropic executes the search, filters results using code execution during searches, and returns the results directly"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key benefits"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"No client-side execution"},{"type":"text","text":": You don't write code to run searches"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Code execution during searches"},{"type":"text","text":": Filters results before they reach users, improving relevance"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Enabled by default"},{"type":"text","text":": Available in the Claude API without extra configuration"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to use it vs. alternatives"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Scenario"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use web search"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use web fetch"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"General research/news"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✓"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Finding credible sources"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✓"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fetching specific page HTML"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✓"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Getting full page content"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✓"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The tool was released alongside "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude Sonnet 4.6"},{"type":"text","text":" in February 2026 as part of Anthropic's advanced tool use improvements."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Do you want the exact API syntax for a specific language (Python, JavaScript, etc.) or details about how to customize search behavior?"}]}]}}
